responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "76EC870346BAFA60E271C397283F06CF", "You were never here, I swear on it. Please spare us. Take what you need from here, and we won\'t send any trouble your way. It\'s not much, I know, but this is all I have. Please just spare us our lives, it\'s all we have.")
